= Introduction
The purpose of this project is to experiment with parallel architecture and computing,
networking and systems design, as well as expand our understanding of the linux operating
system. This project is open to any contributers within the Linux club at KSU (referred
to as LCKSU from now on).

== Structure
In this document we include an index of computers used, as well as a series of tests
and software used. Some software was developed by members of LCKSU, most was not. If
there are any questions on the structure or technology used in this project, reach
out on our discord or through github issues.

